install pip to RHEL (if not already installed by default on RHEL):
  sudo dnf upgrade -y
  sudo dnf install python3-pip  
  pip3 --version
  
 install ipython in virtual environment:
   cd .venv
   source bin/activate
   cd ..
   pip3 install ipython
   
 turn on interactive ipython shell:
   ipython
   
  
  
